Tracker for async updates of golang-googlecode-goauth2 for rawhide and other fedora distribution.
As golang devel packages are used only as a build-time dependency at the moment, this tracker keeps updates and other information about this package, e.g. broken dependencies, exceptions, important pieces of information and other issues.

Please go to the following url: https://admin.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-EPEL-2015-6556/golang-googlecode-goauth2-0-0.7.hgb5adcc2.el6 then log in and leave karma (feedback).
